Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哪都找不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳已经出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他可能已经回住处去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,莫塞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.34,0:00:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,莫塞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你也去找卡尔曼了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧
